About
-----
This is an openid consumer application with auto-signup via merb-auth's built in openid support.

Community
---------
Please fork and keep up to date.  

Requirements
------------
% sudo gem install merb -v=0.9.11

Design
------
Design by Dieter Schneider via oswd.org

